  44: { 'id': 44, 'height': 8, 'weight': 86, 'sprite': 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/44.png', 'artwork': 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/other/official-artwork/44.png', 'abilities': ['Chlorophyll', 'Stench'], 'stats': { 'hp': 60, 'attack': 65, 'defense': 70, 'special-attack': 85, 'special-defense': 75, 'speed': 40 }, 'flavorText': 'The fluid that oozes from its mouth isn\'t drool. It is a nectar that is used to attract prey.', 'evolutionChains': [[{ 'id': 43, 'name': 'Oddish' }, { 'id': 44, 'name': 'Gloom', 'condition': 'Lv. 21' }, { 'id': 45, 'name': 'Vileplume', 'condition': 'Use Leaf Stone' }], [{ 'id': 43, 'name': 'Oddish' }, { 'id': 44, 'name': 'Gloom', 'condition': 'Lv. 21' }, { 'id': 182, 'name': 'Bellossom', 'condition': 'Use Sun Stone' }]] },
  45: { 'id': 45, 'height': 12, 'weight': 186, 'sprite': 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/45.png', 'artwork': 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/other/official-artwork/45.png', 'abilities': ['Chlorophyll', 'Effect Spore'], 'stats': { 'hp': 75, 'attack': 80, 'defense': 85, 'special-attack': 110, 'special-defense': 90, 'speed': 50 }, 'flavorText': 'The larger its petals, the more toxic pollen it contains. Its big head is heavy and hard to hold up.', 'evolutionChains': [[{ 'id': 43, 'name': 'Oddish' }, { 'id': 44, 'name': 'Gloom', 'condition': 'Lv. 21' }, { 'id': 45, 'name': 'Vileplume', 'condition': 'Use Leaf Stone' }], [{ 'id': 43, 'name': 'Oddish' }, { 'id': 44, 'name': 'Gloom', 'condition': 'Lv. 21' }, { 'id': 182, 'name': 'Bellossom', 'condition': 'Use Sun Stone' }]] },
